HEADWORD: Alcoholate
<hw>Al"co*hol*ate</hw> <pr>(⟦acr⟧l"k⟦osl⟧*h⟦ocr⟧l*⟦asl⟧t)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F. <ets>alcolaie</ets>.]</ety>
